      "description": "Ready to roll without the premium price tag? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it's fully drivable and gets you where you need to go dependably! You'll notice some visible wear and minor imperfections consistent with its age, but the mechanicals are solid and it handles the road well. A great opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer who wants reliable transportation without overpaying. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
