      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to give you a clear, honest picture of what you can expect. The exterior shows its age \u2014 there are several visible scratches, some paint fading in areas, and minor dents that are noticeable upon close inspection. The interior is functional but shows significant wear, including worn upholstery, some scuffs on the dashboard trim, and general signs of regular use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some attention \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting into. This is a practical, budget-friendly option for a buyer who is comfortable with a vehicle that needs some TLC and is priced accordingly.",
