    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable everyday transportation at a great value! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs well and handles daily driving duties without a fuss, making it a practical choice for commuters and budget-minded buyers. You'll notice some visible wear on the interior and exterior that reflects its age, along with a few minor imperfections, but nothing that gets in the way of its dependability. If you're looking for a solid, no-frills ride that won't break the bank, this one is worth a look!",
      "price": 15000.0,
